{
  "stem": "19198.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Phillipson invited the five of us to have lunch with him, which was a very delightful and good lunch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And afterwards, after the lunch, he interrupted the flow of the congregate conversation by saying, I noticed you gentlemen in my service last Saturday, and I noticed that you were wearing head coverings.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want you to know that this is not the custom in American Reform Judaism, and I would appreciate your not doing that again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So while Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Morgenstern was more liberal, even though he too was a Classical Reformed Jew, there were many Reform Jews to whom any Orthodox custom was just something that was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did that make you feel?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How-- how did you take that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we were, of course, shocked by it, because we had been in-- in another synagogue where there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And around the Hebrew Union College we had had-- encountered no problem from any of the students or the faculty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just one of the many culture shocks that we had to endure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hebrew Union College.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we were given a full scholarship, including room and board, and an opportunity of doing some work, for which we were paid $0.50 an hour, which at that time was the accepted pay for student labor.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our regular contact was by airmail letter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I must change that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our-- our normal contact was by letter that usually took a week, a week and a half, to cross the-- the ocean.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
